arters of the state government. The protest was summoned by the Popular Front by public transport.\n </p>\n <p>\n  The situation of public transportation of MG has been increasingly denounced by workers by the poor condition. Plattered vehicles, stopped in the middle of the route due to mechanical problems, spoiled air conditioning, leaks, until the absurd of wheels are detached from the moving buses, beats for lack of brakes or even fires in the vehicles for lack of maintenance have already become part of Revolting routine of Morro Alto station users, particularly in the lines of Move as 501C and 503h that make the journey to the central region of the capital and whose tickets cost R $ 7.70. Months ago, protesters\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-passageiros-fecham-estacao-de-onibus-e-denunciam-pessimas-condicoes-na-regiao-metropolitana-da-capital/\">\n   closed the Justin\u00f3polis bus station\n  </a>\n  , also in Vespasian, to denounce the conditions of transport.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169245\" data-id=\"169245\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-300x135.jpeg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-768x345.jpeg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1536x690.jpeg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Imag